  "notes": "Primary data from the official RFEG club page (all 8 rated recorridos: Blancas/Amarillas/Azules/Rojas, each rated for men and women). Stroke index is identical on the RFEG card for all tees and genders (permutation of 1-18 verified; pars sum to 72; each tee's 18 distances sum exactly to its published total). Cross-checked against the club's own hole-by-hole guide (serenagolf.com): hole 3 (par 3, HCP 1, 182/170/131/116 m) and hole 8 (par 4, HCP 9, 292 m amarillas) match RFEG exactly. Discrepancy: golfshake.com lists aggregate 'yards' of 6168 (white) and 5884 (yellow) with front/back 3175/3260, which do not match the RFEG meters (6196/5909, front/back 3071/3125); golfshake appears to use an older or mislabeled card and was not used for hole data. Course designed by Manuel Piñero; water in play on 16 of 18 holes."
